		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Repro steps:&#xD;&#xA;1. Start the game.&#xD;&#xA;2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;3. god on&#xD;&#xA;4. goto 118.74, 50.67, -247.32&#xD;&#xA;5. Move around and killcombat when spectator attacks.&#xD;&#xA;6. Loot Dhourn's corpse.&#xD;&#xA;7. Open the inventory and use the Crystal." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="29" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This dialogue is for an artefact called a Memory Shard, a crystal taken from the Petrified Drow (Dhourn).&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The crystal can store memories - in this case, Dhourn's knowledge of the location of the Adamantine forge. The player either approaches knowing what it is, or can discover its function based on a check. " />
